text: Krajów is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Krotoszyce, within Legnica County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. Prior to 1945 it was Krayn in Germany. The erstwhile manor house of the counts of Schweinitz ==References== Category:Villages in Legnica County
title: Krajów, Lower Silesian Voivodeship
